{"tid":219512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[食物鏈頂端] 百萬蟹軍襲古巴！ 強國網民雀躍：食完丹麥蠔擦肥蟹","createTime":"2017-04-27T09:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T12:04:17.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d44dde15f7f68ff3d19e8067dd602d72d44f8b71","tid":219512,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"丹麥日前傳出海邊生蠔泛濫，讓中國網民想用「舌尖」消滅生蠔。內地媒體昨又報道，古巴豬灣（Bay of Pigs）近日也遭受「蟹禍」，百萬蟹軍驚現路上，集體橫穿馬路，湧向海邊產卵。牠們所到之處，路面全被覆蓋，路人直呼無立足之地。當地居民擔心蟹帶毒，不敢吃牠們，也怕被蟹鉗所傷，只好緊閉大門。不過，這則報道再次讓中國網民歡呼了！<br />\n<br />\n大批網民熱烈討論，不少人留言詢問「能吃嗎？」還有人直呼「可以暑假去丹麥在海邊一邊欣賞美景一邊吃生蠔，十一黃金周再去古巴啃啃秋天的大螃蟹」。有人則表示「生蠔和螃蟹都被我們吃到怕，所以都跑國外定居去了」、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「有本事來入侵中國，分分鐘吃的你變成二級保護動物」！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9461ad522f041d69fd173ef6094440f4efe829ea","tid":219512,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541b210868fff5ca3a6655dd51ba02968a19b448","tid":219512,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"支那班垃圾真係完全唔覺得人地係串緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab69f1b0fb41207a985194d6f9a0d3e3a5386ad5","tid":219512,"uid":47184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那班垃圾真係完全唔覺得人地係串緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自嘲都睇唔出邊個係柒頭都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee73b3ed5067025051fd69c7d8df6b02d9972df","tid":219512,"uid":61752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vistazo.com/sites/default/files/galeria/2017/04/25/2017-04-25t144328z_1872706587_rc1790aa7390_rtrmadp_3_cuba-crabs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvistazo.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fgaleria%2F2017%2F0